description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Packers/Lions game. Are all concerns with the Packers now a thing of the past? Former NFL O-Lineman Tony Boselli calls into assess moral in Jacksonville. And Al Michaels shares his thoughts on the Manning broadcast, as well as listens to Seton's impression of him.
